{"tid":2067591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾國衛:呢幾日不斷有唔同政黨同市民要求提供關愛安排 已經向選管會反映 如果安排唔到等於剝奪他們投票權","createTime":"2020-06-17T05:58:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T08:48:52.000Z","uid":22556,"like":3,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4d302071ec16c9b55bee11b6b08d12a0627f60cd","tid":2067591,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T05:58:46.000Z","msg":"曾國衛在《文匯》訪問中又提到，因應政黨和市民等的意見，已向選管會反映，希望可以為有需要的人士，包括長者、孕婦、殘障人士提供「關愛安排」，讓他們優先投票，指若有需要人士在烈日下，因身體無法支撐放棄投票，等於剝奪他們投票權，「呢樣嘢講唔過去」。<br />\n<br />\n他又表示已向多次向選管會強調要改善選舉安排，為長者孕婦等有需要人士提供「優先投票關愛通道」，認為安排有助選舉公平。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/dq-%E5%89%8D%E5%A5%8F-%E6%94%BF%E5%88%B6%E5%B1%80%E9%95%B7%E6%9B%BE%E5%9C%8B%E8%A1%9B-%E5%8E%9F%E5%89%87%E4%B8%8A-%E6%A0%B9%E6%9C%AC%E4%B8%8A%E5%8F%8D%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95-%E4%B8%80%E5%BF%83%E7%99%B1%E7%98%93%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83-%E4%BB%A4%E4%BA%BA%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E6%95%88%E5%BF%A0%E7%89%B9%E5%8D%80%E6%93%81%E8%AD%B7%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%B3%95/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fdq-%25E5%2589%258D%25E5%25A5%258F-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%2588%25B6%25E5%25B1%2580%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25A1%259B-%25E5%258E%259F%25E5%2589%2587%25E4%25B8%258A-%25E6%25A0%25B9%25E6%259C%25AC%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25BF%2583%25E7%2599%25B1%25E7%2598%2593%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%259C%2583-%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%2590%25A6%25E6%2595%2588%25E5%25BF%25A0%25E7%2589%25B9%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%2593%2581%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E5%259F%25BA%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%25B3%2595%2F&d=3WJ6yD1ie6zkJWt%2B9GiXG80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=610269a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fdq-%25E5%2589%258D%25E5%25A5%258F-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%2588%25B6%25E5%25B1%2580%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%25